【Masamune】 Here's the key. Looks like we can
safely get out of here.

【Masamune】 Hmm, another recording stone has
fallen.

【Leon】 Oh, I wonder what kind of record this is.
Let's take a look right away.

【Masamune】 What should we do if it's Melissa-
sensei again?

【Masamune】 It seems like there's something, but
the flames are burning and I can't get close.
【Masamune】 With water magic...
【Tommy】 I don't think this will disappear.
【Masamune】 What...

【Tommy】 This feeling, it's like the flames of
hell. I wonder if regular water magic won't work.

【Tommy】 It was written in a book that it can be
extinguished with holy water.

【Masamune】 Holy water... I don't have something
like that.

【Masamune】 No, there seemed to be a water source
earlier.
【Masamune】If we pour holy water here...
